# Memory Index

This file is an index of all memory files in the `memory/` directory. Each line points to a memory file that helps your assistant understand your context, preferences, and work patterns.

**Memory persists across sessions.** Use it for:
- Your profile (role, expertise, preferences)
- Validated approaches (what works, why)
- Project context (ongoing work, deadlines, dependencies)
- External references (where to find information)

See guides/02-memory-system.md for comprehensive guidance.

